window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Damien had planned it all out.</b></p> <p>He had the support of his wealthy parents, loyal friends who shared his goals, even a high-ranked Core just waiting for him to use. One more Dungeon run and he would be setâ€“he was finally going to take the first real step on the path to fame and fortune as a Hero. The future was so bright, he needed shades to see it.</p> <p>Was, in the past tense. Because Damien just died.</p> <p>Instead of the pearly gates awaiting him, though, he's been reborn, placed in control of a Dungeon... and now might be a good time for him to reconsider everything he thought he knew about the way the universe works.</p>"; 
